									clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
							</svg>
							Solid Foundation in Gemara & Halacha.
						</dt>
						<dd class="inline font-light"
							>Rebbe Nachman wanted his students to be both Lamdanim
							<span class="italic">and</span> Tzaddikim.
						</dd>
					</div>
					<div class="relative pl-9">
						<dt class="inline font-semibold text-white">
							<svg
								class="absolute left-1 top-1 h-5 w-5 text-indigo-500"
								viewBox="0 0 20 20"
								fill="currentColor"
								aria-hidden="true">
								<path
									fill-rule="evenodd"
									d="M11 2a1 1 0 10-2 0v6.5a.5.5 0 01-1 0V3a1 1 0 10-2 0v5.5a.5.5 0 01-1 0V5a1 1 0 10-2 0v7a7 7 0 1014 0V8a1 1 0 10-2 0v3.5a.5.5 0 01-1 0V3a1 1 0 10-2 0v5.5a.5.5 0 01-1 0V2z"
