							>Our Yeshiva utilizes every means available to experience
							sustained spiritual growth, lasting inspiration, and real
							camaraderie and brotherhood. Whether inside the Beis Medrash or
							out, we intend to experience holiness wherever genuine holiness is
							to be found.
						</dd>
					</div>
				</dl>
			</div>

			<!-- Twe Great Programs-->

			<div class="mx-auto mt-32 max-w-7xl px-6 sm:mt-40 lg:px-8">
				<div class="mx-auto max-w-4xl lg:mx-0">
					<h2 class="text-3xl font-bold tracking-tight text-white sm:text-4xl"
						>Two Distinct Programs in Harmony</h2
					>
					<p class="mt-6 text-lg leading-8 text-gray-300"
						>Within this yeshiva, we offer two exceptional programs that cater
						to diverse needs and backgrounds, each enriching the other through
						shared experiences.</p
					>
				</div>
				<div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 w-full mt-16">
					<!-- Program A-->
					<div
						class="text-white rounded-3xl p-6 ring-1 ring-white/20 xl:p-10 w-full bg-white/10">
						<div class="flex items-center justify-between gap-x-4">
							<h2
								id="tier-freelancer"
								class="text-2xl lg:text-3xl font-semibold leading-8 text-white"
								>The Exploration Program</h2
