							class="mt-4 space-y-3 text-md lg:text-xl font-light tracking-wide text-gray-200 xl:mt-10">
							<p
								>Featuring an equally unique and exciting schedule of daily
								hisbodedus, inspirational classes on Likutei Mohoran amongst
								other classic Chassidic sefarim, and the advanced tools for
								learning Talmud through which every bachur can explore his
								Jewish roots and build spiritual foundations for the rest of his
								adult life.
								<p> </p>

								<h2 class="font-semibold text-xl lg:text-2xl mt-12"
									>The Exploration Program Rabbeim
								</h2>
								<ul
									class="mt-4 space-y-6 text-xl font-light tracking-wide text-gray-200 xl:mt-10">
									<li class="flex">
										<img
											class="aspect-square w-20 h-20 rounded-2xl object-cover"
											src="kalmus.jpg"
											alt
										/>
										<div class="pl-4 flex flex-col justify-center">
											<h3
												class="text-2xl font-semibold leading-8 tracking-wide text-white"
												>R’ David Yisrael Kalmus</h3
											>
											<p class="text-base leading-7 text-gray-300"
												>Rosh Yeshiva, The Exploration Program</p
											>
										</div>
									</li>
									<li class="flex">
										<img
											class="aspect-square w-20 h-20 rounded-2xl object-cover"
											src="yochanan.jpg"
											alt
										/>
										<div class="pl-4 flex flex-col justify-center">
											<h3
												class="text-2xl font-semibold leading-8 tracking-wide text-white"
												>R’ Yochanan Glebocki</h3
											>
											<p class="text-base leading-7 text-gray-300"
												>Mashgiach, The Exploration Program</p
											>
										</div>
									</li>
									<li class="flex">
										<img
											class="aspect-square w-20 h-20 rounded-2xl object-cover"
											src="rothman.jpg"
											alt
										/>
										<div class="pl-4 flex flex-col justify-center">
											<h3
												class="text-2xl font-semibold leading-8 tracking-wide text-white"
												>R’ Ben Tzion Rothman</h3
											>
											<p class="text-base leading-7 text-gray-300"
												>Maggid Shiur, The Exploration Program</p
											>
										</div>
									</li>
								</ul>
								<h2 class="font-semibold text-xl lg:text-2xl mt-12"
									>The Exploration Program Daily Schedule
								</h2>

								<ul
									x-data="{ schedules: [
                { title: 'Morning Seder'},
                { time: '7:00AM', item: 'Shacharit' },
                { time: '8:00AM', item: 'Breakfast' },
                { time: '8:30AM - 9:30AM', item: 'Hitbodedut in Forest of Har Nof' },
