                { time: '10:00AM', item: 'Introductory Gemara Shiur with R\u00B4 Bentzion Rothman' },
                { time: '10:15AM - 11:45', item: 'Gemara Chavruta with R\u00B4 Yochanan Glebocki. R\u00B4 Bentzion Rothman checking in to address unique needs of each individual Chavruta pair and to help advance their personal skills and mastery in Gemara learning' },
                { time: '12:00 PM', item: 'Likutey Moharan with R\u00B4 David Yisrael Kalmus' },
                { time: '1:00 PM', item: 'Lunch Break' },
                 { title: 'Afternoon Seder'},
                { time: '2:00PM', item: 'Choose Your Own Learning Interest with R\u00B4 Yochanan Glebocki, R\u00B4 Bentzion Rothman, R\u00B4 Noam Elbaz, and other available Exploration Staff members. Additionally, on specific days of his choosing, Va\u00B4ad will be led by R\u00B4 Yochanan Glebocki' },
